00:22:33,606 --> 00:22:38,471
dos hobn mir zikh opgeshtelt di ershte, in ⟨COSĂUȚer⟩ vald. SOROCA,

418
00:22:38,471 --> 00:22:39,995
⟨COSĂUȚer⟩ vald.

419
00:22:41,503 --> 00:22:43,235
un,

420
00:22:45,267 --> 00:22:48,568
mir hobn ibergenekhtikt, s'iz geven yene nakht in dem vald.

421
00:22:48,608 --> 00:22:51,639
dort hot men oysgeshtelt shisn un dort hot men geshlogn.

422
00:22:51,831 --> 00:22:54,639
un in der fri zenen mir vayter gegangen.

423
00:22:54,700 --> 00:22:56,651
mir zenen aribergegangen dem Nyester.

424
00:22:56,792 --> 00:22:58,282
zenen mir ongekumen

425
00:22:58,282 --> 00:22:59,554
keyn YAMPOL'.

426
00:23:02,074 --> 00:23:04,538
YAMPOL' iz geven ibern Nyester.

427
00:23:05,972 --> 00:23:08,160
di mentshn vos m'hot getribn,

428
00:23:08,470 --> 00:23:10,978
zey hobn zikh dokh gemuzt ergets opshteln.

429
00:23:11,187 --> 00:23:12,868
flegn zikh opshteln

430
00:23:13,161 --> 00:23:17,803
in di kolkhozn, vayl di, in di KONYUSHNI, dort vu di ferd, vu dos alts.

431
00:23:17,803 --> 00:23:19,349
zey hobn dokh gemuzt; in shtiber

432
00:23:19,349 --> 00:23:21,215
hobn mir zikh dokh nisht gekent.

433
00:23:22,122 --> 00:23:24,849
hot er gefunen di kolkhozn, di rusishe,

434
00:23:25,227 --> 00:23:27,077
vos zenen geven leydik,

435
00:23:27,758 --> 00:23:29,349
di, ⟨z-⟩,

436
00:23:29,349 --> 00:23:32,749
un dortn hot men undz arayngetribn un tsunoyfgetribn.

437
00:23:32,749 --> 00:23:35,819
mir hobn ge- ibergenekhtikt un vayter gegangen.

438
00:23:35,819 --> 00:23:37,606
azoy ⟨zenen m-⟩ hot men undz getribn.

439
00:23:37,647 --> 00:23:39,308
ver hot aykh bavakht?

440
00:23:39,351 --> 00:23:41,133
daytshn mit rumener.

441
00:23:42,304 --> 00:23:44,002
rumener un daytshn.

442
00:23:45,173 --> 00:23:46,280
mit hint.

443
00:23:46,725 --> 00:23:49,844
azoy vi ir hot gezen di, di, dos o.

444
00:23:49,844 --> 00:23:54,527
m'hot nisht getort geyn oyf der zayt. m'hot nisht getort geyn oyf yener zayt. m'hot gedarft geyn glaykh.

445
00:23:54,527 --> 00:23:56,979
m'hot zikh nisht getort a sakh opshteln.

446
00:23:57,137 --> 00:23:58,745
host ⟨dikh⟩ opgeshtelt,

447
00:23:58,745 --> 00:24:00,337
hostu bakumen petsh.

448
00:24:00,546 --> 00:24:03,881
du host gemuzt geyn, un ver es hot nisht gekent iz geblibn oyfn veg.

449
00:24:04,933 --> 00:24:06,575
geyendik oyfn veg

450
00:24:06,575 --> 00:24:10,364
hob ikh shoyn oykh nisht gekent geyn. hot der tate mikh genemen oyfn d- oyf der pleytse.

451
00:24:10,364 --> 00:24:12,589
er hot genemen mayn bruder oyf der pleytse.

452
00:24:12,865 --> 00:24:15,407
er hot nisht gevust er zol undz farshlepn.

453
00:24:15,447 --> 00:24:17,769
un azoy, dorf tsu dorf.

454
00:24:17,995 --> 00:24:21,805
 s'iz do, in di derfer,

455
00:24:21,805 --> 00:24:25,273
gedenk ikh, shtark, miese kolkhozn,

456
00:24:25,273 --> 00:24:28,113
vos, dos heyst, azoy vi,

457
00:24:28,170 --> 00:24:30,513
 s'iz nisht kolkhoz

458
00:24:30,513 --> 00:24:36,315
vos m'hot geboyt. m'hot ar- ⟨tr-⟩ poshet, di mentshn arayngetribn, zoln dervayl...

459
00:24:37,165 --> 00:24:39,454
ver s'iz dortn take geblibn,

460
00:24:39,612 --> 00:24:43,571
vos zenen ⟨VOOB-⟩ nisht gekent mer geyn zenen shoyn dortn farblibn,

461
00:24:43,763 --> 00:24:47,807
un ver se hot nokh gekri- gekrokhn, hot men getribn vayter.

462
00:24:48,910 --> 00:24:53,460
dort iz geven oykh a tsivile bafelkerung, nisht keyn yidishe tsivile bafelkerung?

463
00:24:52,200 --> 00:24:54,843
⟨n- ⟩, neyn! dos iz nisht... nor yidn!

464
00:24:53,820 --> 00:24:55,417
farlozte kolkhozn?

465
00:24:54,900 --> 00:24:57,816
dos iz geven kolkhozn eygns di yidn,

466
00:24:57,816 --> 00:24:59,479
v- di vos me traybt,

467
00:24:59,625 --> 00:25:02,204
azoy vi s'iz geven AUSCHWITZ,

468
00:25:02,204 --> 00:25:04,440
farmakht d- v- di, di ale...

469
00:25:04,440 --> 00:25:08,947
m'hot arayngetribn in dem o. dos iz geven di kolkhozn. s'iz nisht geven kolkhozn,

470
00:25:08,947 --> 00:25:10,687
vos m'hot, mentshn gelebt.

471
00:25:10,687 --> 00:25:11,901
dos iz geven

472
00:25:11,901 --> 00:25:14,088
far di mentshn, far di yidn,

473
00:25:14,088 --> 00:25:16,721
az zey zoln kenen, zey zoln nekhtikn,

474
00:25:16,721 --> 00:25:19,000
un zayn a por teg, un me traybt zey vayter.

475
00:25:19,000 --> 00:25:20,527
un dortn zoln zey shtarbn.

476
00:25:20,905 --> 00:25:22,957
dos iz geven di kolkhozn.

477
00:25:22,761 --> 00:25:25,185
vi hot men zikh an eytse getun mitn esn?

478
00:25:24,904 --> 00:25:28,603
vos heyst, es-? vos ir hot gehat, hot ir gegesn. hot ir nisht gehat, zent ir geshtorbn.

479
00:25:28,603 --> 00:25:29,538
vos far a esn?

480
00:25:29,538 --> 00:25:31,057
m'hot aykh gegebn esn?

481
00:25:31,671 --> 00:25:34,374
vos ir hot gekent, m'hot,

482
00:25:34,374 --> 00:25:36,119
funem feld vos m'iz gegangen, me,

483
00:25:36,119 --> 00:25:39,317
az m'hot gekent khapn a burikl, m'hot gekent khapn

484
00:25:39,317 --> 00:25:40,918
a bisl vaser, dos,

485
00:25:40,918 --> 00:25:44,101
⟨m'- oder⟩ s'iz epes geven oyf tsu... nisht geven,...

486
00:25:44,580 --> 00:25:46,700
zenen mir ongekumen keyn,

487
00:25:46,740 --> 00:25:51,394
 YAM-, YAMPOL'. KRYZHOPOL' iz geven a stantsye.

488
00:25:51,394 --> 00:25:52,610
un ales

489
00:25:52,610 --> 00:25:54,683
in azoyne farmakhte lagern.

490
00:25:54,874 --> 00:25:58,867
s'iz farmakhte kolkh- dos hot geheysn kolkhoz, ober dos iz geven lagern.

491
00:26:00,021 --> 00:26:04,908
in OBODIVKA zenen mir ongekumen, hobn mir getrofn a groyse umglik.

492
00:26:04,982 --> 00:26:07,708
vos heyst umglik? mentshn zenen shoyn lang geven dortn,

493
00:26:07,708 --> 00:26:09,212
zenen friert aroys.

494
00:26:09,252 --> 00:26:11,237
s'iz geven a sakh fun Basarabye,

495
00:26:11,665 --> 00:26:14,641
vos m'hot zey friert, getribn.

496
00:26:14,641 --> 00:26:18,393
dos iz dokh geven... nisht oyf eyn mol hot men genemen di yidn un m'hot zey getribn;

497
00:26:18,393 --> 00:26:19,920
m'hot zey teylvayz,

498
00:26:19,920 --> 00:26:22,626
tsu toyznt, toyznt finef hundert mentshn.

499
00:26:23,207 --> 00:26:29,401
m'hot gezogt, di gas, in der gas, vifl es iz geven, azoy fil hot men tsunoyfgenemen.

500
00:26:29,417 --> 00:26:32,046
az mir zenen ongekumen keyn OBODIVKA,

501
00:26:32,046 --> 00:26:35,683
dort hobn mir gezen... in yedn kolkhoz hobn mir gezen

502
00:26:35,683 --> 00:26:37,657
mentshn vos, geshtorbene,

503
00:26:37,657 --> 00:26:42,356
ge- vos zey kenen shoyn nisht geyn. az zey hobn nisht gekent geyn, hot men zey,

504
00:26:42,356 --> 00:26:44,492
 der-, hot men zey derharget

505
00:26:44,492 --> 00:26:45,814
oyfn plats.

506
00:26:45,921 --> 00:26:51,694
un di vos zey hobn nokh gekent geyn zenen gegangen un zey hobn gemuzt geyn. m'hot zey geshlogn un zey zenen gegangen.

507
00:26:52,823 --> 00:26:57,634
mir zenen ongekumen in OBODIVKA. dort iz geven a sakh toyte dort. dort iz geven

508
00:26:57,634 --> 00:27:01,306
dray KONYUSHNIs, dray KONYUSHNI fun di ferd, fun di khazeyrim.

509
00:27:01,306 --> 00:27:03,278
iz dort geven a sakh mentshn,

510
00:27:03,278 --> 00:27:04,629
tsunoyfgetribene.

511
00:27:04,838 --> 00:27:06,958
in dem OBODIVKA

512
00:27:07,555 --> 00:27:10,097
iz, iz mayn m- tate's bruder.

513
00:27:10,812 --> 00:27:12,426
tate's bruder.

514
00:27:12,432 --> 00:27:15,851
hot men im, iz er gegangen, m'hot, ⟨hot⟩

515
00:27:15,851 --> 00:27:20,323
⟨fu-⟩ un dort iz av- iz avekgegangen mayn tate's shvester, di Ester-Rivke,

516
00:27:20,650 --> 00:27:21,876
mit a zun

517
00:27:22,607 --> 00:27:26,735
fun, tsvontsik yor... ⟨es⟩ iz dort geshribn vifl bay aykh...

518
00:27:27,366 --> 00:27:31,629
un, un a froy. dos iz Ester-Rivke mitn man, mitn kind.

519
00:27:31,737 --> 00:27:33,300
un er iz gegangen.

520
00:27:33,542 --> 00:27:35,358
er,

521
00:27:35,398 --> 00:27:38,733
 der, bruder, dem tate's.

522
00:27:39,128 --> 00:27:41,180
un dan iz geven a shvester.

523
00:27:41,727 --> 00:27:43,362
zi heyst ⟨Halm⟩...

524
00:27:43,362 --> 00:27:45,686
kh'hob ge- ikh hob mikh dermont: zi heyst ⟨Halm⟩...

525
00:27:46,266 --> 00:27:49,348
mit, oykh a zun, mit a man.

526
00:27:49,405 --> 00:27:51,272
⟨keyns⟩ nisht geblibn fun zey.

527
00:27:53,100 --> 00:27:57,464
un mir f- zenen gegangen vayter. m'hot undz vayter getribn.

528
00:27:54,006 --> 00:27:54,746
dos,

529
00:27:57,370 --> 00:28:02,344
dos alts iz geshen ven?, s'iz shoyn geven vinter eyn un fertsik, tsvey un fertsik?

530
00:28:00,610 --> 00:28:02,142
vinter!

531
00:28:02,142 --> 00:28:03,996
 dos iz geshen

532
00:28:04,626 --> 00:28:05,835
far,

533
00:28:05,925 --> 00:28:09,142
far, CHRISTMAS.

534
00:28:10,077 --> 00:28:12,231
s'iz shoyn geven frest,

535
00:28:13,165 --> 00:28:14,357
kalt,

536
00:28:14,937 --> 00:28:18,238
un ikh hob gem- un mir zenen, azoy zenen mir gegangen on...

537
00:28:18,238 --> 00:28:22,524
vos mir hobn gehat hobn mir gekent ho-, d- mir hobn dokh nisht gekent mitnemen keyn zakhn.

538
00:28:22,665 --> 00:28:25,133
un geshlofn zenen mir oyf der erd.

539
00:28:25,197 --> 00:28:29,989
on k- UNK m'hot gornisht gehat, azoy ⟨hob-⟩ azoy iz, ⟨azoy⟩, s'iz geven,

540
00:28:29,989 --> 00:28:33,185
azoy hobn mir zi-, vayl Hitler hot gezogt in "MEIN KAMPF",

541
00:28:33,185 --> 00:28:34,972
az me darf undz nisht shisn,

542
00:28:34,972 --> 00:28:39,079
nor me darf un- me darf der mentsh azoy, di yidn darfn zikh mutshen

543
00:28:39,220 --> 00:28:42,572
un, un zoln, bakumen ⟨den,⟩ toyt.

544
00:28:42,679 --> 00:28:44,607
un dos hot er getun mit undz.

